Description: # CTML
        (Color Text Markup Language)
        
        
        ```python
        
        from trml import format
        
        
        string = """
        My Normal Text
        <text color="red" on="black">Some characters</text>
        """
        
        
        colored = format(string)
        
        print(colored)
        
        ```
        
